  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "       ===== Erromite Intel =====\n\n   Workers: Small pink erromites
    with a\n                   nasty habit of destroying key\n                  
    infrastructure. Poses no threat\n                   to personnel.\n\n    Soldiers:
    Large red erromites that attack\n                   personnel on sight. Maintaining\n                  
    distance is advised.\n\nSwarmers : Winged brown erromites that\n                   
    spit corrosive orbs at personnel.\n                    Eliminate with extreme
    prejudice."
