      m_Calls: []
  m_text: '===== Mission Brief =====


    Three swarms of erromites have been spotted
    in this region of the Gaea Cyberspace.


    Locate the center platform and plant
    the patch generator to begin debugging.


    Eliminate erromites with your standard
    issue debugging tool to feed power to the patch generator.


    Do not allow
    the erromites to destroy the patch generator, or else the mission will fail.'
